name: YourMorningMinute
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Welcome to Your Morning Minute! 

Get grounded and feel focused for your day! Listen every morning to this daily flash briefing.

Created and produced by Josie Ong of the Affirmation Pod podcast.

Music by Chris Collins at IndieMusicBox.com

A note for listeners: there are 24 recordings that are re-ordered in batches of 8 and then published again.

All recordings are also available on podcast players and the Affirmation Pod app, available on the Apple and Google Play app stores!

Download the free app at AffirmationPodApp.com

Thanks for listening to Your Morning Minute, see you tomorrow!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
